  <brief_title>Octreotide as Palliative Therapy for Cancer-Related Bowel Obstruction That Cannot Be Removed by Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Octreotide for Palliation of Inoperable Bowel Obstruction: A Phase II Study</official_title>
